at movie, if the same people reviewed it who reviewed this one. it seems like, if the movie's director is totally off his rocker, or if it's a french movie with sex and subtitles, or if it's a cartoon, it is going to get great reviews, hands down, anything else is boring and has already been done. blah, bring on the boring please!

